Package: linmic
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-pyside6, pipewire, pipewire-pulse, pulseaudio-utils, adb
Description: Use an Android phone as a PipeWire microphone
 LinMic receives low-latency microphone audio from an Android phone over USB
 and exposes it as a virtual microphone source through PipeWire.
